Package: updateR
Type: Package
Title: Package development toolkit
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2011-08-01
Author: Mark Cowley <m.cowley@garvan.org.au>
Maintainer: Mark Cowley <m.cowley@garvan.org.au>
Description: A collection of functions that enable R package
    maintainers to build and update packages. A shell script
    essentially runs roxygen, R CMD CHECK & BUILD & INSTALL. Tools for
    refreshing a currently loaded library are included, as well as
    finding the dependencies of any function.
Depends: R (>= 2.12.0), codetools, roxygen
Suggests: Rd2roxygen
URL: http://pwbc.garvan.unsw.edu.au
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
Collate: 'available.packages.bioc.R' 'edit.func.R' 'find.src.file.R'
    'get.full.path.R' 'get.function.dependencies.R' 'import.function.R'
    'is.dir.R' 'list.my.packages.R' 'mjc2roxygen.R' 'relibrary.R'
    'trim.R' 'unlibrary.R' 'updateR-package.R' 'updateR.R'
    'which.package.R'
